  <h1>About LinkForge</h1>

  <p class="legal-badge">About Our Platform</p>

  <p class="legal-subtitle">
    Simple link management, QR generation and analytics in one place.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>

  <p>
    LinkForge was built to make sharing links easier, cleaner and more
    effective. Long URLs can be difficult to manage and share, so
    LinkForge provides a simple way to create short links, generate QR
    codes and monitor engagement through analytics.
  </p>

  <h2>What LinkForge Offers</h2>

  <p>
    Users can create short URLs, generate QR codes instantly and track
    link activity through a centralized dashboard. The platform is
    designed to keep link management straightforward without unnecessary
    complexity.
  </p>

  <h2>Who It's For</h2>

  <p>
    LinkForge is suitable for creators, students, businesses, marketers
    and anyone who regularly shares links online or offline.
  </p>

  <h2>Core Principles</h2>

  <p>
    <strong>Simplicity:</strong> Useful tools should be easy to use.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Reliability:</strong> Links should remain accessible whenever
    they are needed.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Privacy:</strong> User data should be handled responsibly and
    securely.
  </p>

